143
00:07:05,300 --> 00:07:06,100
Yes.

144
00:07:06,100 --> 00:07:09,800
And I encourage teenage mothers
to stay in school.

145
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:11,500
Are you kidding me?

146
00:07:11,500 --> 00:07:15,200
No, I am not
kidding you, Ricky.

147
00:07:15,200 --> 00:07:18,700
I encourage you
to take responsibility

148
00:07:18,700 --> 00:07:21,100
