157
00:07:45,700 --> 00:07:48,000
Or at least she doesn't
want me to see her.

158
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:49,700
Is that crazy, or what?

159
00:07:49,700 --> 00:07:51,300
She's scared, Ben.

160
00:07:51,300 --> 00:07:53,900
I mean she's scared and she's
angry and she's overwhelmed.

161
00:07:53,900 --> 00:07:59,100
Do her and yourself a favor and go
along with the plan, whatever it is.

162
00:07:59,100 --> 00:08:01,200
Of course, whatever it is is
probably gonna change 

163
00:08:01,200 --> 00:08:02,800
over and over and over again.

164
00:08:02,800 --> 00:08:04,700
It's just not easy, that's all.

165
00:08:04,700 --> 00:08:07,600
What in life is easy?
Not much, that's what.

166
00:08:08,400 --> 00:08:10,200
Certainly not
the sausage business.

167
00:08:10,300 --> 00:08:12,900
Come on,
we better get going.

168
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:13,900
Dad...

169
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:16,700
