217
00:10:19,200 --> 00:10:21,300
Just don't care if they know.
Don't care.

218
00:10:21,300 --> 00:10:25,100
You can decide that, you know,
to not care what people think.

219
00:10:25,100 --> 00:10:26,600
Who doesn't care
what people think?

220
00:10:26,600 --> 00:10:28,100
Me. I don't care.

221
00:10:28,100 --> 00:10:31,000
Come on, Amy. At least consider
going back to school.

222
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:33,100
I'll be right there with you,
holding your hand.

223
00:10:33,100 --> 00:10:34,900
