226
00:10:40,800 --> 00:10:43,700
You can come over tonight
and say goodbye if you want.

227
00:10:43,700 --> 00:10:45,400
I'll probably leave
in the morning.

228
00:10:45,400 --> 00:10:46,400
No.

229
00:10:46,400 --> 00:10:50,300
Thanks for asking, but, no,
I don't wanna say goodbye,

230
00:10:50,300 --> 00:10:54,100
