00:11:08,600 --> 00:11:10,100
It's me.

233
00:11:13,700 --> 00:11:14,800
What are you doing here?

234
00:11:14,800 --> 00:11:16,200
Come on,
let's stay home today.

235
00:11:16,200 --> 00:11:17,100
I can't.

236
00:11:17,100 --> 00:11:18,000
Why?

237
00:11:18,000 --> 00:11:19,300
'Cause I don't want to.

238
00:11:19,500 --> 00:11:22,300
All right. Can I stay here?

239
00:11:22,500 --> 00:11:24,300
I'm not in the mood
to go to school today.

240
00:11:24,300 --> 00:11:25,400
You can't stay here.

241
00:11:25,400 --> 00:11:26,400
Is your mom home?

242
00:11:26,400 --> 00:11:27,500
You know she's not.

243
00:11:27,500 --> 00:11:30,200
Come on, Adrian. I can't
go to school today.

244
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:30,600
I can't.

245
00:11:30,600 --> 00:11:32,500
